responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "DA061D304B42A94F83EF9792850EE2A6", "By the seven! I certainly hope Scribe Monroe wrote down this discovery. Goblins North of Carphin? Hmm, I\'m certain there\'s more to this note, especially since it was meant for the goblins. I wonder if this has something to do with those strange masked fellows some of our researchers have seen out near Carphin. They\'re very aggressive and attack anyone on sight out there. It\'s very dangerous!")
